Class RestOptions.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.api.rest.RestOptions.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    RestOptions

    public static final class RestOptions.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility that can be used to configure and construct immutable instances of the RestOptions.Builder, by chaining fluent configuration method calls.
